## CRITICAL: DO NOT modify any Japanese text content (repeated for emphasis)

## Project
Dr.ストレッチ認定トレーナー副業マッチングプラットフォーム

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15 (App Router) + TypeScript
- shadcn/ui + Tailwind CSS v4
- Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth)
- Server Actions for data mutations

## Design Tokens
- Primary Red: #E60012 (use `primary` in Tailwind)
- Accent Green: #DADF00 (use `accent` in Tailwind)
- Font: Montserrat (headings), Inter (body), Noto Sans JP (Japanese)
- Border radius: Card 12px, Button/Input 8px, Badge 16px (pill)

## Coding Rules
1. TypeScript strict mode — no `any` types
2. Functional components only
3. Server Components by default, `"use client"` only when needed
4. Use shadcn/ui components from `@/components/ui/`
5. Import Server Actions from `@/actions/`
6. Import types from `@/types/`
7. Use `@/lib/supabase/` for DB access
8. No inline styles — use Tailwind classes
9. Responsive design: mobile-first
10. All forms use react-hook-form + zod validation

## File Structure
```
src/app/(trainer)/   — Trainer-facing pages
src/app/(store)/     — Store manager pages
src/app/(hr)/        — HR control panel
src/app/(auth)/      — Login/Register
src/actions/         — Server Actions
src/components/ui/   — shadcn/ui components
src/components/shared/ — App-level shared components
src/types/           — TypeScript type definitions
src/lib/supabase/    — Supabase client utilities
```

## User Roles
- `trainer` → (trainer)/ routes
- `store_manager` → (store)/ routes
- `hr` → (hr)/ routes

## Component Patterns
- Card-based layouts for lists
- Table for admin/HR data views
- Badge for status indicators
- Sheet for mobile navigation
- Dialog for confirmations
- Sonner for toast notifications

## DO NOT
- Create new UI primitives (use shadcn/ui)
- Use `any` type
- Query Supabase directly in components
- Hardcode colors (use CSS variables/Tailwind)
- Skip form validation
- Modify Japanese text content
